Datuk Lamri Ali bụbu onye nduzi nke Sabah Parks
Na December 1999 World Conservation Union (IUCN) nke nzukọ mpaghara nke e mere na Pakse, Laos,Enyere Ali ihe nrite WCPA-IUCN Fred M
Ihe nrite a na-amata ntinye aka ya na nchekwa ihe okike na mmegharị mpaghara echedoro na Malaysia
Datuk Lamri bụ naanị onye Malaysia nwetara ihe nrite aonyinye a.
A na-akpọ Nepenthes × alisaputrana, ngwakọta nke ụdị osisi abụọ a ma ama na Bornean pitcher, iji sọpụrụ ya.
